description:
Money, sex, or love? If your last night on earth was just beginning - what would you do? This strange, dark comedy follows the lives of a handful of Eastern European villagers for a week as strange events unfold in their small village. The village idiot, whose principal goal is to own his own motorbike, predicts the future while ogling the gypsy girls at the local carnival. The mayor prepares for an EU delegation, cheats on his wife, and attends his weekly cardgame - his last! Other village oddballs include a philandering barber, strange doctor and nurse, a priest who sleeps in a coffin, drug dealers, junkies, gypsies, midgets and smugglers ... something for just about any taste! And then, there is the Russian beauty Nadia (Veronica Zemanova) whose daily walk to work turns every head in the village. Imagine the surprise when they discover that she is working as an exotic dancer at nearby night spot! Dark comedy with more than a few very good sight gags. Gypsy circus performers doing a striptease on whirl-a-gig carnival ride is not to be missed. But most of all there is Veronika Zemanova, who gets a lot of screen time to show off her angelic face (and more).

